"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

"==================== Mappings =========================
"
" Better split switching
map <C-j> <C-W>j
map <C-k> <C-W>k
map <C-h> <C-W>h
map <C-l> <C-W>l

" Fast saving
nmap <leader>w :w!<cr>

""" Make navigation in quickfix window easier
"map <C-n> :cnext<CR>
"map <C-m> :cprevious<CR>

nmap <leader>n :tabnext<CR>
nmap <leader>p :tabprevious<CR>

""" closing quickfix window
nnoremap <leader>a :cclose<CR>

"""""""""" ack.vim plugin 
cnoreabbrev Ack Ack!
nnoremap <Leader>f :Ack!<Space>


"""""""""" Highlight the current word under cursor with <leader>*
nnoremap <leader>* :<C-u>let @/ = expand('<cword>')<cr>

"""""""""" Visual block, cause <C-v is not working with current mappings
command! VisualBlock execute "normal! \<C-v>"

